==English==
===Noun===
'''timepiece'''
# Any [[device]] that [[measure]]s or [[register]]s [[time]]; a [[clock]] or [[watch]].

====Usage Note====
*Strictly, a timepiece is a timekeeping instrument that lacks a striking mechanism (e.g., a bell, chimes, or gong) to announce the passage of time. One with a striking mechanism is a [[clock]]. This distinction is, however, mostly lost in usage.

